You can control Vimar VIEW Product devices with voice commands.
Ask Alexa to view the live feed of the camera in your living room or turn on/off your power adapter. 
All you have to do is talk to Alexa but first you have to complete the following simple steps:

(1)Download our Vimar VIEW Product app from Google Play or from the iOS App Store.
(2)Sign up for a MyVIMAR account (if you already have an account, log in directly) in our Vimar VIEW Product app;
(3)Now turn on your devices and connect them to the Vimar VIEW Product app;
(4)Configure the devices in our Vimar VIEW Product app and change their name accordingly, since they will then be used in the Vimar VIEW Product Skill;
(5)Download Amazon Alexa app from Google Play or from the iOS App Store.
(6)Configure Echo with the Alexa app;
(7)Search Vimar VIEW Product in the Alexa list of Skills;
(8)Click on enable Vimar VIEW Product Skill and you will be redirected to the MyVIMAR login page;
(9)Enter your Vimar account username and password;
(10)The settings are now complete.

Now you can enjoy voice control and see the live feed of your cameras on your Echo devices with screens: “Alexa, show me living room”
